title: Beck (musician) - Live Recordings - Bootleg Collection 1994-2000
description:
A great collection of live recordings from the golden era of Beck. Most are soundboard or FM/TV broadcast recordings. A couple of the earlier ones might be audience recordings.

Most files are mp3, but there are a few concerts in VQF format. A free VQF plugin is available for Winamp. It's an older, now obsolete format that was briefly popular in the late 1990s.
